WEBVTT

00:00.801 --> 00:03.637
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:32.366 --> 00:35.736
Lydia: NICOLE, STOP!

00:35.736 --> 00:37.171
NICOLE!

00:37.171 --> 00:40.674
[ BOTH PANTING ]

00:43.711 --> 00:46.580
I RUINED EVERYTHING.

00:46.580 --> 00:47.848
[ CRYING ]

00:47.848 --> 00:49.783
LET ME HELP YOU.

00:49.783 --> 00:50.918
OKAY?

00:50.918 --> 00:52.286
I CAN HELP YOU.

00:52.286 --> 00:54.422
AAH!
UGH!

00:54.422 --> 00:56.390
[ SIREN WAILING ]
AH, SHIT.

00:56.390 --> 00:57.925
UGH.

00:57.925 --> 00:59.627
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

01:01.061 --> 01:02.830
NICO--

01:02.830 --> 01:05.466
L.A.P.D. OFFICERS SPEND EVERY
SHIFT TRYING TO HELP PEOPLE

01:05.466 --> 01:07.635
WHO OFTEN DON'T EVEN KNOW
THEY NEED HELP.

01:07.635 --> 01:10.771
SOME DAYS THE TRYING WORKS
BETTER THAN OTHERS.

01:12.072 --> 01:14.275
[ RETCHING ]

01:24.152 --> 01:26.154
[ RETCHING CONTINUES ]

01:26.154 --> 01:28.789
[ COUGHS ]

01:31.058 --> 01:32.059
[ SIGHS ]

01:32.059 --> 01:34.228
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]

01:37.431 --> 01:40.634
[ MOUTHWASH SWISHING,
WATER RUNS ]

01:41.835 --> 01:43.437
[ SIGHS ]

01:49.210 --> 01:51.545
BREAKFAST WILL BE READY
IN A MINUTE.

01:51.545 --> 01:53.447
YOU WANT TO SET
THE TABLE?

01:53.447 --> 01:54.882
MM, I'M NOT HUNGRY.

01:56.284 --> 01:58.186
YOU SICK AGAIN?

01:58.186 --> 02:00.521
YOUR BRAS DON'T FIT,

02:00.521 --> 02:05.559
AND YOUR MOOD'S
MOODIER THAN USUAL, SO...

02:06.660 --> 02:08.862
...WHEN WERE YOU
GONNA TELL ME?

02:11.899 --> 02:13.967
ALL RIGHT.
[ SIGHS ]

02:13.967 --> 02:15.236
36 YEARS OLD.

02:15.236 --> 02:18.972
YOU DON'T HAVE TO TELL
YOUR MOTHER ANYTHING.

02:18.972 --> 02:22.443
BUT WHATEVER
YOU WANT TO DO...

02:22.443 --> 02:24.278
I'M HERE FOR YOU.

02:24.278 --> 02:26.447
MOM, WHATEVER
I WANT TO DO?

02:26.447 --> 02:28.982
WELL, YOU --
YOU HAVE CHOICES.

02:28.982 --> 02:31.419
AND WHATEVER YOU DECIDE,

02:31.419 --> 02:34.154
I'M GONNA BE FINE
WITH IT.

02:34.154 --> 02:37.458
WOW. [ SIGHS ]

02:37.458 --> 02:40.194
I SO WASN'T EXPECTING THAT.
[ SCOFFS ]

02:40.194 --> 02:42.863
WELL...
I'M CONFUSED.

02:42.863 --> 02:46.900
I MEAN, I KNOW THAT YOU
HAVE ALWAYS WANTED THIS,

02:46.900 --> 02:48.302
BUT...

02:48.302 --> 02:50.904
ALONE?

02:50.904 --> 02:52.706
YOU DID IT.

02:52.706 --> 02:55.309
[ SCOFFS ]
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE.

02:55.309 --> 02:58.312
AND I WAS TEACHING --
HOME BY 4:00.

02:58.312 --> 03:01.815
WHY IS IT THAT WITH MEN,
NO ONE'S QUESTIONING THEM?

03:01.815 --> 03:05.653
THE MALE DETECTIVES,
THEY DON'T HAVE TO MAKE CHOICES.

03:05.653 --> 03:08.922
[ Chuckling ] WELL,
THEY'RE NOT HAVING THE BABIES,

03:08.922 --> 03:10.491
THEIR WIVES ARE.

03:10.491 --> 03:14.562
AND YOU'RE IN THE WORLD
THAT YOU WANTED TO BE IN.

03:14.562 --> 03:16.597
WHEN THE GIRLS
YOU WENT TO SCHOOL WITH

03:16.597 --> 03:18.366
WERE DATING
AND HAVING BABIES,

03:18.366 --> 03:19.733
YOU WERE LEARNING ABOUT

03:19.733 --> 03:23.704
CORPSES AND BLOOD-SPATTER
PATTERNS...

03:23.704 --> 03:25.439
DETECTIVE.

03:26.874 --> 03:30.278
SO [SIGHS]

03:30.278 --> 03:32.946
WHO'S THE FATHER?

03:32.946 --> 03:35.283
[ SIGHS ]

03:41.889 --> 03:42.756
Man: GIVE ME THAT!

03:42.756 --> 03:44.258
Woman:
LEAVE ME ALONE. STOP!

03:44.258 --> 03:45.626
I WANT THAT!
HEY, HEY, HEY!

03:45.626 --> 03:47.094
OKAY, FINE.
YOU WANT IT, YOU TAKE IT!

03:47.094 --> 03:48.896
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

03:48.896 --> 03:49.897
IS THERE A PROBLEM?

03:49.897 --> 03:52.966
OH, MY GOD.
GEEZ.

03:54.802 --> 03:55.836
YOU ALL RIGHT?

03:55.836 --> 03:57.738
THANK YOU.
WOW, THANK YOU SO MUCH.

03:57.738 --> 03:58.539
YEAH.

03:58.539 --> 03:59.707
I'M BEN.
I LIVE, UH...

03:59.707 --> 04:01.475
YEAH, YOU'RE
IN MY BUILDING, RIGHT?

04:01.475 --> 04:02.976
YEAH.
I'VE SEEN YOU AROUND.

04:02.976 --> 04:04.011
YEAH.
I'M CATHY.

04:04.011 --> 04:05.145
HEY.
NICE TO MEET YOU.

04:05.145 --> 04:06.246
IS THAT YOUR BOYFRIEND?

04:06.246 --> 04:07.448
EX.
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH?

04:07.448 --> 04:09.182
RECENT BREAKUP. YEAH.
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:09.182 --> 04:10.751
SHIT,
WHAT DO THEY WANT?

04:10.751 --> 04:12.753
HEY, GUYS.
UH, WE'RE GOOD.

04:12.753 --> 04:15.356
THANKS.
HAVE A GOOD ONE, ALL RIGHT?

04:15.356 --> 04:16.357
TAKE CARE.

04:16.357 --> 04:18.826
THANKS.

04:18.826 --> 04:20.528
FUCKING COPS, RIGHT?

04:20.528 --> 04:23.130
DID YOU HEAR ABOUT THAT COP
WHO PUNCHED THAT GIRL...

04:23.130 --> 04:24.865
LIKE, FOR ABSOLUTELY
NO REASON?

04:24.865 --> 04:26.500
FUCKED UP, RIGHT?

04:26.500 --> 04:28.869
YEAH. YEAH.
THAT'S FUCKED UP.

04:28.869 --> 04:31.171
[ RETCHING ]

04:31.171 --> 04:33.607
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]

04:39.513 --> 04:43.351
HEY, UH, YOU HAVE A TAMPON
OR SOMETHING?

04:43.351 --> 04:45.018
UH, YEAH.

04:45.018 --> 04:48.221
THEY NEVER FIX IT WHEN THEY SAY
THEY'RE GONNA FIX IT, YOU KNOW?

04:48.221 --> 04:49.390
THANKS.

04:49.390 --> 04:51.659
YOU KNOW WHAT?
JUST TAKE THEM.

04:55.028 --> 04:56.664
CONGRATULATIONS?

04:59.433 --> 05:02.002
YOU TELL
THE DEPARTMENT YET?

05:02.002 --> 05:03.671
NO.

05:04.838 --> 05:07.908
WELL, PUT IT OFF UNTIL
YOU CAN'T BUCKLE YOUR BELT.

05:07.908 --> 05:12.212
THEY'LL PUT YOU ON A DESK JOB
FOR THE DURATION.

05:12.212 --> 05:16.316
THAT'S MESSED UP, MAN.
SOMEONE TOOK OUT LUPE.

05:16.316 --> 05:18.486
"ABUELITA,"
THEY CALLED HER.

05:18.486 --> 05:19.720
YOU KNEW HER?

05:19.720 --> 05:21.989
NOT REALLY.
I KNEW OF HER.

05:21.989 --> 05:25.325
SHE WAS ONE OF THOSE OLD WOMEN
WHO KNEW EVERYBODY'S BUSINESS,

05:25.325 --> 05:26.694
VOLUNTEERED AT THE CHURCH,

05:26.694 --> 05:28.862
WENT OUT WITH BLANKETS
ON COLD NIGHTS,

05:28.862 --> 05:32.199
AND SHE WAS, LIKE, THE ONLY
PERSON IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD

05:32.199 --> 05:33.967
THAT EVERYONE LIKED.

05:33.967 --> 05:35.268
NOT EVERYONE.

05:35.268 --> 05:36.604
YEAH.

05:36.604 --> 05:38.739
SHE WAS ACTING LIKE
THE COP WAS THE PROBLEM,

05:38.739 --> 05:41.409
NOT THE ASSHOLE WHO TRIED
TO JACK HER FOR HER ICED TEA.

05:41.409 --> 05:42.810
WHAT?

05:42.810 --> 05:45.012
THE WOMAN FROM THIS MORNING
I WAS TELLING YOU ABOUT.

05:45.012 --> 05:48.782
BOHO ARTISTE TYPES
PAINTING CRAPPY PROTEST ART,

05:48.782 --> 05:51.619
LIVING IN FAUX URBAN SQUALOR
UNTIL DADDY BUYS THEM A HOUSE...

05:51.619 --> 05:52.920
COME ON, MAN.
REALLY?

05:52.920 --> 05:55.055
...IN THE PALISADES
FOR A WEDDING PRESENT.

05:55.055 --> 05:56.890
[ SCOFFS ] UGH.

05:56.890 --> 05:58.759
I MEAN, DID YOU TALK
TO MY REALTOR IN CASTAIC?

05:58.759 --> 06:00.528
[ Chuckling ]
YEAH, I TALKED TO HER.

06:00.528 --> 06:01.895
SHE'S SHOWING ME
A FEW PLACES.

06:01.895 --> 06:03.697
THERE WAS ACTUALLY ONE
THAT I LIKED.

06:03.697 --> 06:05.065
I'M GONNA
CHECK IT OUT AGAIN.

06:05.065 --> 06:07.000
YOU NEED TO SIGN
ON THE DOTTED LINE, BEN.

06:07.000 --> 06:09.002
YOU NEED TO GET THE HELL
OUT OF SILVER LAKE

06:09.002 --> 06:11.739
BEFORE YOU START WORRYING ABOUT
GLUTEN AND DRINKING RAW MILK.

06:11.739 --> 06:13.441
YOU NEED TO BE
WITH YOUR PEOPLE --

06:13.441 --> 06:15.042
YOUR PEOPLE
IN THE HIGH DESERT, BABY.

06:15.042 --> 06:18.446
THAT'S THE PLACE.
LAND OF THE BLUE.

06:18.446 --> 06:20.648
NICE.

06:21.949 --> 06:23.651
WANT BREAKFAST?
MNH-MNH.

06:23.651 --> 06:25.653
YOU SURE?
NO.
NO, THANK YOU.

06:25.653 --> 06:28.856
HEY, UM, I'VE GOT
A DOCTOR'S APPOINTMENT TODAY,

06:28.856 --> 06:31.358
SO YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN
FOR LUNCH.

06:31.358 --> 06:32.760
EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT?

06:32.760 --> 06:35.863
YOU KNOW, WITH THE DOCTOR
AND EVERYTHING?

06:35.863 --> 06:36.864
YEAH.

06:38.131 --> 06:39.399
IT'S JUST A CHECKUP.

06:39.399 --> 06:42.970
HEY. HEY.

06:42.970 --> 06:44.371
WHAT DO WE HAVE?

06:44.371 --> 06:47.908
GUY NAMED BRIAN MONROE, BIG
DOWNTOWN REAL-ESTATE DEVELOPER,

06:47.908 --> 06:49.943
STABBED
ABOUT A DOZEN TIMES.

06:49.943 --> 06:51.579
ONE OF THE WORKERS
FOUND HIM HERE

06:51.579 --> 06:53.447
WHEN THEY OPENED UP
THIS MORNING.

06:55.816 --> 06:58.018
HOO-HOO.

06:59.119 --> 07:00.387
DID SHE SEE ANYTHING?

07:00.387 --> 07:02.289
NO.
CAME IN AND HERE HE WAS.

07:02.289 --> 07:03.524
GIRL LIVES UPSTAIRS.

07:03.524 --> 07:05.225
THE NEIGHBOR SAYS
THE VICTIM

07:05.225 --> 07:08.996
LET HARD-LUCK CASES STAY THERE
SOMETIMES, GAVE THEM A JOB.

07:08.996 --> 07:11.131
[ SIGHS ]

07:16.069 --> 07:18.271
HEY.

07:18.271 --> 07:20.007
DO YOU LIVE UPSTAIRS?

07:22.275 --> 07:24.011
BY YOURSELF?

07:26.880 --> 07:29.082
WHAT'S YOUR NAME,
SWEETIE?

07:29.082 --> 07:31.785
WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME
EVERYTHING YOU SAW?

07:35.789 --> 07:38.592
THIS COFFEE TASTES BURNT.
IT'S BETTER AT GROUNDS FOR --

07:38.592 --> 07:40.160
NO, NO, NO.
ALL RIGHT?

07:40.160 --> 07:43.797
NO COFFEE PLACE WITH NAMES
INVOLVING METAPHORS, JOKES,

07:43.797 --> 07:45.666
OR ANY WORDPLAY
WHATSOEVER.

07:45.666 --> 07:47.267
NO "SUFFICIENT GROUNDS,"

07:47.267 --> 07:50.671
NO "SACRED GROUNDS,"
NO "ESPRESSO YOURSELF."

07:50.671 --> 07:52.540
Man: OFFICER COOPER?
O-OFFICER?

07:52.540 --> 07:54.742
HE'S BACK.

07:54.742 --> 07:57.077
YOU ASK US TO COME
TO THESE COMMUNITY MEETINGS,

07:57.077 --> 08:00.080
AND YOU ACT AS THOUGH YOU CARE,
AND THEN THREE WEEKS LATER...

08:00.080 --> 08:02.215
OKAY, WHAT SEEMS TO BE
THE PROBLEM?

08:02.215 --> 08:03.283
HE'S THE PROBLEM.

08:03.283 --> 08:04.652
YOU SAID
YOU GOT HIM HOUSING.

08:04.652 --> 08:06.486
AND HE'S BACK AGAIN,
PISSING IN MY DOORWAY.

08:06.486 --> 08:07.888
HE'S SCARING AWAY
MY CUSTOMERS.

08:07.888 --> 08:09.590
OKAY, ALL RIGHT.
WE'RE ON IT. OKAY?

08:09.590 --> 08:11.058
THANKS.

08:11.058 --> 08:12.425
[ HORN HONKS ]

08:12.425 --> 08:14.261
WHAT'S YOUR NAME, SIR?

08:14.261 --> 08:15.295
STAN.

08:15.295 --> 08:16.697
STAN. OKAY.

08:21.301 --> 08:23.036
HEY.

08:23.036 --> 08:25.739
HEY, BUDDY.

08:34.214 --> 08:36.049
[ LAUGHS ]

08:36.049 --> 08:37.851
YOU TOOK ME
TO THE SHELTER.

08:37.851 --> 08:39.186
I DID. I DID.
YEAH. YEAH.

08:39.186 --> 08:41.254
WE GOT YOU A PLACE.
WHAT HAPPENED?

08:41.254 --> 08:44.457
YEAH. YEAH.

08:44.457 --> 08:46.193
I-I HAD TO LEAVE.

08:46.193 --> 08:50.463
THEY STOLE MY I.D.,
STOLE MY CART.

08:50.463 --> 08:52.165
I LOST EVERYTHING.

08:52.165 --> 08:54.367
THEY -- THEY WOULDN'T
LET ME BACK IN.

08:54.367 --> 08:55.569
ALL RIGHT, I UNDERSTAND.

08:55.569 --> 08:57.537
BUT YOU CAN'T SLEEP HERE,
ALL RIGHT?

08:57.537 --> 08:58.772
THIS IS PRIVATE PROPERTY.

08:58.772 --> 09:00.540
I-I'M NOT HURTING ANYONE.

09:00.540 --> 09:03.911
HOW ABOUT IF WE, UH,
GIVE HOUSING ANOTHER TRY, HUH?

09:06.513 --> 09:10.818
THEY -- THEY -- THEY --

09:10.818 --> 09:14.755
THEY WON'T LET ME IN
WI-- WITHOUT I.D.

09:16.189 --> 09:17.290
NO.

09:17.290 --> 09:20.327
YOU -- YOU A MARINE?

09:20.327 --> 09:22.162
YES, MA'AM. MARINE.

09:22.162 --> 09:23.997
NICE.

09:23.997 --> 09:26.033
20 YEARS.

09:26.033 --> 09:28.568
SO, IF WE GET YOU
A NEW I.D.,

09:28.568 --> 09:31.304
WILL YOU GIVE HOUSING
ANOTHER TRY?

09:32.572 --> 09:34.307
ANOTHER TRY?

09:34.307 --> 09:35.375
GIVE IT ANOTHER TRY?

09:35.375 --> 09:36.644
ANOTHER TRY?

09:36.644 --> 09:38.211
YEAH. YEAH.

09:38.211 --> 09:39.479
YEAH, I'LL -- YEAH.

09:39.479 --> 09:42.315
WHAT'S YOUR NAME, SIR?
YEAH, YEAH.

09:42.315 --> 09:43.450
TOM.
TOM?

09:43.450 --> 09:44.484
TOM SMITH.

09:44.484 --> 09:46.954
OKAY, TOM SMITH.
TOM SMITH.

09:46.954 --> 09:50.457
WHERE WERE YOU BORN?
THAT'S TOM SMITH.

09:50.457 --> 09:53.060
WHERE WERE YOU BORN,
TOM SMITH?

09:53.060 --> 09:54.795
L.A.

09:57.665 --> 09:59.166
19...

09:59.166 --> 10:01.334
NOVEMBER 25th...

10:01.334 --> 10:05.572
19...40-SOMETHING.

10:05.572 --> 10:07.074
I TALKED TO FERGUSON.

10:07.074 --> 10:07.875
HE'S TALKING?

10:07.875 --> 10:09.109
UH, HE'S BETTER.

10:09.109 --> 10:11.511
STILL A LITTLE HARD
TO UNDERSTAND.

10:11.511 --> 10:12.680
GETTING BETTER --

10:12.680 --> 10:14.281
ALL NEW TEETH,
PLASTIC SURGERY.

10:14.281 --> 10:15.248
IT'S REALLY AN UPGRADE.

10:15.248 --> 10:16.684
WHOA, WHOA.
HOLD ON. HOLD ON.

10:16.684 --> 10:19.086
SEE THIS?
WHOA. HEY!

10:19.086 --> 10:20.353
STOP!

10:20.353 --> 10:22.690
STOP! FREEZE!

10:22.690 --> 10:23.757
BACK, BACK, BACK.

10:23.757 --> 10:25.458
[ SHOUTING IN SPANISH ]

10:25.458 --> 10:28.595
STOP! FREEZE!

10:28.595 --> 10:29.763
I GOT IT. I GOT IT.

10:29.763 --> 10:31.631
YOU ALL RIGHT?
YOU OKAY?

10:31.631 --> 10:33.333
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

10:33.333 --> 10:35.869
[ SIREN WAILING ]

10:38.571 --> 10:40.640
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

10:47.781 --> 10:49.983
[ CLATTER ]

10:53.687 --> 10:55.889
[ OBJECT THUDS ON DUMPSTER ]

11:01.194 --> 11:03.530
COME OUT WITH YOUR HANDS UP!
POLICE!

11:03.530 --> 11:05.999
[ OBJECT THUDS ON DUMPSTER ]

11:14.808 --> 11:16.744
UM, HOW DID YOU END UP
LIVING HERE?

11:16.744 --> 11:18.812
WELL,
BRIAN USED TO COME AROUND

11:18.812 --> 11:21.314
TO WHERE SOME OF US KIDS
WAS CAMPING OUT.

11:21.314 --> 11:23.283
HE'D BRING US
FOOD AND BLANKETS.

11:23.283 --> 11:25.352
SAID IF I WANTED
TO GET OFF THE STREETS,

11:25.352 --> 11:27.420
HE'D GIVE ME A JOB
AND I COULD STAY HERE.

11:27.420 --> 11:31.424
THIS IS TINY.
TINY, THIS HERE'S THE COPS.

11:31.424 --> 11:32.760
YOU LIVE HERE, TOO?

11:32.760 --> 11:35.695
DID YOU HEAR ANYTHING
THIS MORNING AROUND 5:00?

11:35.695 --> 11:37.064
MAYBE SEE SOMEBODY?

11:37.064 --> 11:39.833
Lydia: DID MR. MONROE
LIVE HERE WITH YOU GUYS?

11:39.833 --> 11:42.635
NO, UH,
HE LIVED OVER IN VENICE.

11:42.635 --> 11:44.637
Melanie: NO, I-I NEED A REFILL
ON HER PILLS TODAY.

11:44.637 --> 11:48.408
NICOLE AND HER MOM, MELANIE,
THEY LIVE HERE ALL THE TIME.

11:48.408 --> 11:51.611
YEAH, I-I-I KNOW.
SHE LOST THEM AGAIN.

11:51.611 --> 11:53.046
PSST.
YEAH?

11:53.046 --> 11:56.483
YEAH, I'M DETECTIVE ADAMS.
THIS IS DETECTIVE ROBINSON.

11:56.483 --> 11:58.986
YOU'RE MELANIE, RIGHT?

11:58.986 --> 12:00.720
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

12:00.720 --> 12:01.922
WHOA.
WAIT -- WAIT A MINUTE!

12:01.922 --> 12:03.556
WAIT!
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY!

12:03.556 --> 12:05.558
I'M ABOUT TO KILL HER!

12:05.558 --> 12:08.628
I'LL CUT YOUR THROAT, BITCH!
WHAT'S GOING ON?!

12:08.628 --> 12:10.730
SHE KILLED HIM!
SHE KILLED BRIAN!

12:10.730 --> 12:11.999
Nicole: NO, I DIDN'T!

12:11.999 --> 12:14.101
DON'T YOU SAY
ANOTHER WORD.

12:15.202 --> 12:16.736
I DID IT.

12:16.736 --> 12:20.240
I KILLED BRIAN.

12:33.753 --> 12:35.022
Ben: YOU SHOT A DOG?

12:35.022 --> 12:36.990
IT CAME AT ME
FROM BEHIND THE DUMPSTER.

12:36.990 --> 12:38.225
I CALLED THE AMBULANCE.

12:38.225 --> 12:40.060
Woman:
THEY KILLED A DOG?

12:40.060 --> 12:41.962
HE'S NOT DEAD.
STAND BACK.

12:41.962 --> 12:43.964
NOTHING TO SEE HERE!
GO!

12:45.833 --> 12:46.967
DON'T ASK.

12:46.967 --> 12:48.701
JUST HELP ME OUT,
ALL RIGHT?

12:48.701 --> 12:49.803
OKAY.

12:49.803 --> 12:50.938
CALL THE SERGEANT
FOR ME?

12:50.938 --> 12:52.305
OH, NO, NO, NO.

12:52.305 --> 12:54.341
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO SHOT
MAN'S BEST FRIEND.

12:54.341 --> 12:55.408
[ MAN LAUGHS ]

12:55.408 --> 12:57.244
YOU SEE WHAT YOU CAUSED
BY RUNNING, HUH?

12:57.244 --> 12:59.612
YOU SEE
WHAT YOU CAUSED HERE?!

12:59.612 --> 13:02.349
FUCKING PUNK.
LOOK AT THIS.

13:02.349 --> 13:04.084
IN THE P.C.s.
WHAT IS THAT?

13:04.084 --> 13:05.585
"PERUVIAN CONQUISTADORS."

13:05.585 --> 13:06.820
IS THAT A GANG?

13:06.820 --> 13:08.321
OH, YEAH.
THEY WISH THEY WERE A GANG.

13:08.321 --> 13:11.091
BUNCH OF LOSERS AND GEEKS
TRYING TO BE TOUGH GUYS, RIGHT?

13:11.091 --> 13:12.459
TRYING TO BE TOUGH GUYS?

13:12.459 --> 13:14.862
YOU KNOW WHO THE CONQUISTADORS
WERE, RIGHT?

13:14.862 --> 13:16.063
THEY'RE NOT PERUVIAN.

13:16.063 --> 13:17.264
I AIN'T NEED YOU
TO TELL ME THAT.

13:17.264 --> 13:18.565
AT LEAST I DIDN'T SHOOT
NO DAMN DOG.

13:18.565 --> 13:20.700
YEAH, YOU GOT A FUCKING
PROBLEM WITH ME?!

13:20.700 --> 13:23.070
HUH?!
SAMMY, CHILL OUT, MAN.

13:29.609 --> 13:31.078
IS HE GONNA BE ALL RIGHT?

13:31.078 --> 13:32.645
I'M NOT A VET, SAMMY.

13:32.645 --> 13:35.148
THERE'S A CLINIC ON BEVERLY.
YOU SHOULD TAKE HIM THERE.

13:35.148 --> 13:38.451
NO, WE -- WE -- WE GOT TO WAIT
HERE FOR R.H.D. TO SHOW UP.

13:38.451 --> 13:40.253
WE HAVE PEOPLE
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO BE SAVING.

13:40.253 --> 13:41.554
WHAT ABOUT
ANIMAL CONTROL?

13:41.554 --> 13:43.290
OH, REALLY?
HILL FOR A -- FOR A STRAY?

13:43.290 --> 13:44.724
THEY'RE JUST
GONNA PUT HIM DOWN.

13:44.724 --> 13:45.959
YOU WANT ME
TO PUT HIM DOWN?

13:45.959 --> 13:48.761
COME ON, MAN.
YOU CAN TAKE HIM FOR ME.

13:48.761 --> 13:50.864
JUST DROP HIM OFF
AND TELL THEM

13:50.864 --> 13:53.266
THAT WE'LL BE THERE
AS SOON AS WE CAN.

13:53.266 --> 13:56.403
ALL RIGHT.
TWO LAKERS TICKETS.

13:56.403 --> 13:57.404
OH, COME ON.

13:57.404 --> 13:58.771
ALL RIGHT. OKAY.

13:58.771 --> 14:00.307
[ SIGHS ]
DONE.

14:00.307 --> 14:02.575
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
MY LAKERS TICKETS,

14:02.575 --> 14:03.776
I'LL TELL YOU THAT MUCH.

14:03.776 --> 14:05.578
WHEN DID YOU FIGURE OUT

14:05.578 --> 14:08.949
YOUR DAUGHTER WAS SLEEPING
WITH MR. MONROE?

14:13.386 --> 14:15.555
I DIDN'T PLAN
ON KILLING BRIAN.

14:15.555 --> 14:19.659
I-I JUST SAW RED, AND I GRABBED
THE CLOSEST THING TO ME.

14:19.659 --> 14:21.394
I GUESS IT WAS A KNIFE.

14:21.394 --> 14:23.530
YOU GOT KIDS?

14:24.898 --> 14:26.533
NO.

14:28.235 --> 14:33.006
GOD GIVES YOU
THE TEST YOU NEED.

14:33.006 --> 14:36.476
SO NICOLE WAS THAT TEST?

14:36.476 --> 14:40.613
SINCE THE DAY SHE WAS BORN,
NICOLE WAS HOWLING LIKE A DEMON.

14:40.613 --> 14:44.317
SITTERS COULDN'T HANDLE HER.
SCHOOLS KEPT KICKING HER OUT.

14:44.317 --> 14:47.487
I GOT THROWN OUT OF ONE
APARTMENT AND THEN ANOTHER.

14:47.487 --> 14:51.324
BETWEEN
TAKING HER TO DOCTORS

14:51.324 --> 14:54.962
AND [SIGHS] PICKING HER UP
WHEN SHE WAS IN TROUBLE,

14:54.962 --> 14:57.530
I-I COULDN'T KEEP A JOB.

14:58.999 --> 15:00.333
WHEN BRIAN FOUND US,

15:00.333 --> 15:03.103
WE WERE SLEEPING BEHIND
A 7-ELEVEN UP ON SUNSET.

15:03.103 --> 15:05.538
WHAT'S WRONG WITH NICOLE?

15:05.538 --> 15:08.508
[ CHUCKLES ] EVERY DOCTOR'S
GOT SOMETHING DIFFERENT --

15:08.508 --> 15:12.779
YOU KNOW,
ATTACHMENT DISORDER,

15:12.779 --> 15:14.314
DEFIANT OPPOSITIONAL
DISORDER,

15:14.314 --> 15:16.783
ADHD,
BORDERLINE PERSONALITY.

15:16.783 --> 15:18.418
TAKEN EVERY PILL THERE IS.

15:18.418 --> 15:23.590
ONE MAKES HER SLEEP ALL DAY,
ANOTHER MAKES HER SEE THINGS.

15:23.590 --> 15:27.027
BRIAN WAS THE CLOSEST THING
TO A FATHER SHE EVER HAD,

15:27.027 --> 15:29.229
AND I NEVER --
I NEVER THOUGHT --

15:29.229 --> 15:31.598
HE WAS -- HE WAS KIND,
HE WAS GENTLE.

15:31.598 --> 15:34.534
NICOLE HAD NEVER HAD A MAN
LIKE THAT IN HER LIFE BEFORE,

15:34.534 --> 15:36.103
AND I...

15:36.103 --> 15:38.705
[Voice breaking]
AND I TRUSTED HIM.

15:38.705 --> 15:41.108
AND HE...

15:42.442 --> 15:45.178
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN,
YOU KNOW?

15:47.280 --> 15:49.682
I GUESS I JUST
DIDN'T WANT TO SEE.

15:49.682 --> 15:52.019
WHAT ELSE CAN BE USED
TO ESTABLISH IT?

15:52.019 --> 15:53.286
YOU WANT ME TO DRIVE?

15:53.286 --> 15:55.288
JUST WHILE
YOU'RE ON THE PHONE?

15:55.288 --> 15:59.126
NO -- OKAY. SO HE DOES THAT
AT THE SOCIAL SECURITY OFFICE?

15:59.126 --> 16:01.861
NO, HE DOES NOT HAVE
A BIRTH CERTIFICATE.

16:01.861 --> 16:03.230
OH, GOD.
CRAZY BOB. CRAZY BOB.

16:03.230 --> 16:04.931
THIS IS MY CAR.
HEY, BUDDY.

16:04.931 --> 16:06.433
CAN YOU JUST -- CAN YOU PLEASE
GET ON THE PAVEMENT?
THIS IS MY CAR!

16:06.433 --> 16:07.834
YEAH, YOU NEED TO GET
ON THE CURB.

16:07.834 --> 16:10.503
THIS IS MY CAR!

16:10.503 --> 16:11.904
HEY.
WHAT --

16:11.904 --> 16:13.006
CALM DOWN.

16:13.006 --> 16:14.207
OH, GOD.
SOCIAL SECUR--

16:14.207 --> 16:15.475
YOU NEED TO CALM DOWN.
ALL RIGHT?

16:15.475 --> 16:17.310
HE DOES NOT --
YOU CALM! YOU CALM!

16:17.310 --> 16:19.579
NO, I SAID HE DOES NOT --
PLEASE STEP ON THE CURB!

16:19.579 --> 16:21.648
BOB.
NO, HE'S A HOMELESS MAN,
NOT A-A DOG.

16:21.648 --> 16:22.915
WHY WOULD HE HAVE A --

16:22.915 --> 16:24.684
IF YOU DON'T CALM DOWN,
I'M GONNA HAVE TO BRING YOU IN.

16:24.684 --> 16:26.386
HE DOES NOT HAVE
VACCINATION RECORDS.

16:26.386 --> 16:27.654
YOU MEAN
YOU WISH YOU COULD.

16:27.654 --> 16:29.922
I'M INVISIBLE.
YOU CAN'T SEE ME.

16:29.922 --> 16:30.923
AAH!

16:30.923 --> 16:33.126
OH! YOU CAN SEE ME!

16:33.126 --> 16:34.561
I CAN SEE YOU, BOB.

16:34.561 --> 16:37.597
I LOVE THIS CAR!
IT SMELLS LIKE APPLE PIE!

16:37.597 --> 16:39.466
OH, YOUR HAND
IS SO SMOOTH!

16:39.466 --> 16:40.500
MY HANDS?

16:40.500 --> 16:42.935
NO, HERS!
YOURS IS TOTALLY CALLOUSED.

16:42.935 --> 16:45.938
LIKE YOUR SOUL.
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

16:45.938 --> 16:48.208
[ SIGHS ]

16:48.208 --> 16:50.910
NO IDEA
WHO HE BELONGS TO?

16:50.910 --> 16:53.846
NO COLLAR.
I FIGURE HE'S A STRAY.

16:53.846 --> 16:55.082
[ DOG PANTING ]

16:55.082 --> 16:56.683
HE GONNA BE ALL RIGHT?

16:56.683 --> 16:57.917
NOT WITHOUT SURGERY.

16:57.917 --> 17:00.520
YOU SHATTERED HIS FEMUR
AND NICKED AN ARTERY.

17:01.921 --> 17:03.923
BUT YOU CAN FIX HIM.

17:03.923 --> 17:06.693
SURGERY'S EXPENSIVE.

17:06.693 --> 17:08.395
NO OWNER...

17:10.963 --> 17:12.132
SO...

17:12.132 --> 17:13.700
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN
TO HIM?

17:13.700 --> 17:17.104
WELL, HE'S AN ELDERLY
MIXED-BREED DOG

17:17.104 --> 17:19.172
WITH A HISTORY
OF VIOLENCE.

17:19.172 --> 17:21.007
SO YOU'RE JUST GONNA
LET HIM DIE?

17:21.007 --> 17:24.077
WE'LL MAKE HIM COMFORTABLE,
THEN PUT HIM TO SLEEP.
RIGHT.

17:24.077 --> 17:25.412
HE WON'T SUFFER.

17:25.412 --> 17:27.914
MAKE HIM COMFORTABLE
BY STICKING A NEEDLE IN HIM,

17:27.914 --> 17:29.249
THEN MURDER HIM?

17:29.249 --> 17:31.218
[ PANTING CONTINUES ]

17:35.155 --> 17:37.224
HOW MUCH?

17:38.491 --> 17:39.826
[ LAUGHS ]
1,300 BUCKS?

17:39.826 --> 17:42.095
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO --
LET THEM MURDER HIM?

17:42.095 --> 17:43.963
[ CHUCKLES ]
SO WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

17:43.963 --> 17:45.098
YOU GONNA TAKE HIM HOME?

17:45.098 --> 17:46.566
[ CHUCKLES ]
MAYBE. I DON'T KNOW.

17:46.566 --> 17:48.535
WHAT, ARE WE FUCKING
ANIMAL CONTROL, MAN?

17:48.535 --> 17:50.503
THE MUTT WAS ATTACKING YOU.

17:50.503 --> 17:52.772
NO, R.H.D.
ALREADY INVESTIGATED IT.

17:52.772 --> 17:55.875
OFFICER BRYANT RESPONDED
TO THE THREAT APPROPRIATELY.

17:55.875 --> 17:56.909
R.H.D., F.I.D. --

17:56.909 --> 17:58.178
I SHOT A KID LAST YEAR,

17:58.178 --> 18:00.380
THOSE FUCKERS
DIDN'T SHOW UP THAT FAST.

18:00.380 --> 18:02.449
YOU REMEMBER THAT?
DOWN ON ALVARADO STREET?

18:02.449 --> 18:03.850
LAST YEAR?
YEAH, MAN.

18:03.850 --> 18:05.852
I WAS ON ALVARADO STREET,
THIS FUCKING SHOOTOUT.

18:05.852 --> 18:08.388
KID COMES RUNNING OUT
IN THE MIDDLE OF IT -- "AAH!"

18:08.388 --> 18:09.822
I BLEW HIS FUCKING
THUMB OFF.

18:09.822 --> 18:11.858
HE GOT A NICE SETTLEMENT, TOO.
BELIEVE ME.

18:11.858 --> 18:15.262
HE'S NOW GOING TO ONE OF
THE BEST PRIVATE SCHOOLS
ON THE WEST SIDE,

18:15.262 --> 18:16.796
COMPLIMENTS
OF THE L.A.P.D.

18:16.796 --> 18:17.897
[ LAUGHS ]

18:17.897 --> 18:19.866
SHIT FUCKING HAPPEN
TO ALL OF US, MAN.

18:56.002 --> 18:58.938
Doctor: HOW LONG AGO
WAS YOUR LAST PERIOD?

18:58.938 --> 18:59.939
THREE MONTHS.

18:59.939 --> 19:01.741
YOUR FIRST PREGNANCY?

19:01.741 --> 19:03.142
SECOND.

19:03.142 --> 19:06.145
I HAD A MISCARRIAGE
A FEW YEARS AGO.

19:06.145 --> 19:07.714
CAUSE?

19:07.714 --> 19:08.815
NOTHING IN PARTICULAR.

19:08.815 --> 19:11.284
MY DOCTOR AT THE TIME
SAID IT WAS NORMAL.

19:11.284 --> 19:15.188
IT IS, BUT IT MEANS YOU HAVE AN
INCREASED RISK IN MISCARRYING,

19:15.188 --> 19:16.623
ESPECIALLY GIVEN YOUR AGE.

19:16.623 --> 19:18.858
ARE YOU PLANNING
ON CARRYING TO TERM?

19:18.858 --> 19:20.893
UH, IS ABORTION
STILL AN OPTION?

19:20.893 --> 19:24.197
TERMINATING A PREGNANCY'S
STILL PRETTY STRAIGHTFORWARD

19:24.197 --> 19:25.365
UP TO 16 WEEKS.

19:25.365 --> 19:28.100
I CAN MAKE YOU
AN APPOINTMENT.

19:28.100 --> 19:31.037
UM, I WAS JUST WONDERING.

19:31.037 --> 19:36.609
IF YOU DECIDE TO CARRY TO TERM,
KNOW THAT AFTER 35,

19:36.609 --> 19:39.746
YOU HAVE AN INCREASED RISK
IN BIRTH DEFECTS,

19:39.746 --> 19:41.781
DOWN SYNDROME
BEING THE MOST COMMON.

19:41.781 --> 19:44.016
GIVEN YOUR LOW LEVELS
OF BODY FAT,

19:44.016 --> 19:47.454
I'M SURPRISED YOU WERE
ABLE TO CONCEIVE WITHOUT HELP.

19:47.454 --> 19:50.257
IT MAY BE DIFFICULT
TO DO AGAIN.

19:50.257 --> 19:51.958
WITH YOUR RISK
FOR MISCARRIAGE,

19:51.958 --> 19:54.461
YOU MIGHT WANT TO TAKE
A LEAVE OF ABSENCE.

19:54.461 --> 19:57.163
IT'S UNLIKELY IT WILL BE
THIS EASY TO CONCEIVE AGAIN

19:57.163 --> 19:58.265
IF YOU LOSE THIS ONE.

19:58.265 --> 19:59.566
YEAH.

19:59.566 --> 20:03.803
WELL, I'M NOT PLANNING
ON TAKING ANY TIME OFF.

20:03.803 --> 20:04.804
OKAY, THEN.

20:04.804 --> 20:08.207
LET'S GET YOU UP
IN THE STIRRUPS.

20:09.141 --> 20:10.510
THERE'S THAT.

20:14.781 --> 20:16.816
[ SIGHS ]

20:20.520 --> 20:21.954
I PAY 2 GRAND A MONTH.

20:21.954 --> 20:23.923
YOU PAY 2 GRAND A MONTH
TO LIVE IN THAT SLUM?

20:23.923 --> 20:25.858
I WILL HAVE YOU KNOW
I LIVE NEXT DOOR

20:25.858 --> 20:28.395
TO THE GIRL WHO PLAYS BASS
ON "THE CONAN SHOW."

20:28.395 --> 20:30.263
THOUGHT YOU ALREADY
HAD A DOG.

20:30.263 --> 20:31.798
WELL, MY EX HAS HIM...

20:31.798 --> 20:34.901
ALONG WITH MY KID
AND EVERYTHING ELSE.

20:34.901 --> 20:36.736
YOUR BALLS.

20:36.736 --> 20:38.338
LOOK AT THIS.

20:38.338 --> 20:41.408
TWO MORE LITTLE GEEKS
THINK THEY'RE IN A GANG.

20:41.408 --> 20:43.543
PROBABLY CAME HERE
WHEN MATH CLUB LET OUT.

20:43.543 --> 20:44.911
SAME GANG?
YEAH.

20:44.911 --> 20:46.946
THERE'S GOT TO BE A REASON
THEY'RE ALL OUT.

20:46.946 --> 20:48.981
READY, GRANDMA?

20:48.981 --> 20:51.017
[ ENGINE REVS ]

20:51.017 --> 20:52.752
NOW.

20:52.752 --> 20:54.220
HEY, FELLAS!

20:54.220 --> 20:55.422
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

20:58.658 --> 21:00.427
WHERE'S THE OTHER GIRL?

21:00.427 --> 21:02.161
IN THE BATHROOM.

21:02.161 --> 21:03.996
THERE'S NO BATHROOM
IN THERE!

21:08.034 --> 21:09.035
HOW --

21:09.035 --> 21:12.038
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

21:15.207 --> 21:16.509
HEY.

21:16.509 --> 21:18.511
YEAH, I DON'T THINK
IT WAS THE MOTHER.

21:18.511 --> 21:21.013
AND I THINK
I REALLY SCREWED UP.

21:23.883 --> 21:24.884
OH.

21:25.785 --> 21:26.919
PARTNER.

21:26.919 --> 21:27.787
WHOA.

21:27.787 --> 21:30.122
YOU GOT THE SAME
ON YOU, HUH?

21:30.122 --> 21:31.190
HUH?

21:31.190 --> 21:32.525
NAH, HE'S CLEAN.

21:32.525 --> 21:33.926
YEAH, SET HIM FREE.
ALL RIGHT.

21:33.926 --> 21:35.695
LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE
THE CATCH OF THE DAY, KID.

21:35.695 --> 21:37.464
I DON'T KNOW WHETHER
TO GRILL OR FRY YOU.

21:37.464 --> 21:39.599
COME ON, MAN.
GIVE ME A BREAK.

21:39.599 --> 21:42.735
WHY WOULD I DO THAT?
IT'S A PRETTY SERIOUS CRIME.

21:42.735 --> 21:45.004
THAT'S A LOT
OF WEED, MAN.

21:45.004 --> 21:47.940
IT'S A LOT OF OREGANO.
THAT STILL SELLS.
IT'S STILL A CRIME.

21:47.940 --> 21:49.476
YOU WANT
TO GET OUT OF THIS,

21:49.476 --> 21:51.077
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO GIVE US
SOMETHING RIGHT NOW.

21:51.077 --> 21:53.145
I AIN'T GOT NOTHING.
YOU AIN'T GOT NOTHING?

21:53.145 --> 21:56.616
THREE OF YOU MORONS
OUT ON THE SAME DAY?
SOMETHING'S GOING ON.

22:00.753 --> 22:02.288
WHAT ARE WE
LOOKING AT HERE?

22:02.288 --> 22:04.724
WE'RE LOOKING AT JAIL TIME,
RIGHT?
OH, YEAH.

22:04.724 --> 22:06.393
GET IN THE CAR.
OKAY, WAIT, MAN.

22:06.393 --> 22:08.861
I'LL TELL YOU WHO SHOT
ABUELITA, MAN, OR
WHATEVER THEY CALL HER.

22:08.861 --> 22:10.363
KID NAMED
JOSE RAFAEL, MAN.

22:10.363 --> 22:12.231
WE WERE SUPPOSED TO BE
SHOOTING AT MS-13.

22:12.231 --> 22:13.400
WE GOT BEEF WITH THEM.

22:13.400 --> 22:14.734
YOU AIN'T GOT BEEF
WITH NOBODY

22:14.734 --> 22:16.335
'CAUSE NOBODY CARES ENOUGH
TO HAVE BEEF WITH YOU.

22:16.335 --> 22:19.138
YEAH, WELL, NOW THEY KNOW.

22:19.138 --> 22:20.973
EVERYONE KNOWS.

22:20.973 --> 22:22.108
WE NO JOKE.

22:22.108 --> 22:23.510
NO JOKE. [ SCOFFS ]

22:23.510 --> 22:25.445
NO JOKE?

22:25.445 --> 22:29.382
YOUR BOY SHOT GRANDMA MOSES,
YOU FUCKING IDIOT.

22:31.418 --> 22:33.986
SO WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN
TO ME?

22:35.254 --> 22:38.758
LET'S SEE WHAT SHE SAYS.

22:43.996 --> 22:48.000
WE FOUND THAT ITEM OF CLOTHING
WITH BLOOD ON IT.

22:48.000 --> 22:50.537
WE THINK
IT'S YOUR DAUGHTER'S.

22:50.537 --> 22:52.405
Melanie: IT'S MINE.

22:52.405 --> 22:55.307
WE ALSO PULLED PRINTS
OFF THE KNIFE.

22:55.307 --> 22:57.544
THOSE WEREN'T YOURS.

23:01.548 --> 23:03.015
NICOLE RAN AWAY.

23:03.015 --> 23:05.818
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHERE SHE MIGHT BE?

23:07.487 --> 23:09.522
MELANIE, YOU'RE NOT
DOING HER ANY FAVORS.

23:09.522 --> 23:10.890
IF YOU KNOW
WHERE SHE IS --

23:10.890 --> 23:12.992
YOU DON'T NEED TO FIND HER.
I DID IT.

23:13.926 --> 23:16.028
WE ALSO TALKED TO PEOPLE
AT THE CAFГ©.

23:16.028 --> 23:19.432
THEY SAID THAT NICOLE CAN BE
UNPREDICTABLE, VIOLENT.

23:19.432 --> 23:21.468
THEY DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT MY DAUGHTER.

23:21.468 --> 23:23.035
YEAH, BUT WE KNOW
SHE HAS PROBLEMS,

23:23.035 --> 23:25.071
AND THE JUDGE WILL TAKE THAT
INTO ACCOUNT.

23:25.071 --> 23:26.138
A JUDGE?

23:26.138 --> 23:28.708
MY BABY IS NOT GOING BEFORE
SOME JUDGE.

23:28.708 --> 23:29.976
SHE HAS A FUTURE.

23:29.976 --> 23:32.845
YOU SEE THE PAINTINGS
IN THE APARTMENT?

23:32.845 --> 23:34.313
ALL HERS.

23:34.313 --> 23:35.948
SEE, A LOT OF ARTISTS
ARE -- ARE --

23:35.948 --> 23:37.684
THEY'RE TROUBLED,
TEMPERAMENTAL.

23:37.684 --> 23:39.586
AN ART TEACHER
IN HER LAST SCHOOL

23:39.586 --> 23:41.854
SAID SHE WAS GOOD AS ANYONE
TWICE HER AGE.

23:41.854 --> 23:45.424
SHE'S 15,
OUT ON THE STREETS.

23:45.424 --> 23:48.495
DON'T YOU THINK
WE SHOULD FIND HER

23:48.495 --> 23:50.530
BEFORE SOMETHING
HAPPENS TO HER?

23:52.599 --> 23:54.400
[ SIGHS ]

23:54.400 --> 23:55.768
WELL...

23:55.768 --> 23:58.437
NO, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT UNIT HE SERVED WITH.

23:58.437 --> 24:00.006
Cooper: SHIT.

24:00.006 --> 24:01.207
YOU'RE THE MARINE.

24:01.207 --> 24:03.409
I THOUGHT THAT YOU WOULD HAVE
THAT INFORMATION.

24:03.409 --> 24:05.111
WHAT CAN WE DO FOR YOU?
[ SIGHS ]

24:05.111 --> 24:08.114
D.B. -- FIGURED YOU'D WANT
TO SECURE FOR YOUR DETECTIVES.

24:08.114 --> 24:09.148
OUR DETECTIVES?

24:09.148 --> 24:11.618
LOOKS TO ME
LIKE HE'S ON COUNTY LAND.

24:11.618 --> 24:13.486
YOU GUYS STILL HANDLE
THE RAIL, RIGHT?

24:13.486 --> 24:14.754
YOU GUYS STILL HANDLE
EVERYTHING ELSE.

24:14.754 --> 24:15.955
YEAH, I'LL HOLD.
RIGHT?

24:15.955 --> 24:17.223
[ LAUGHS ]

24:17.223 --> 24:20.493
I DON'T KNOW, PAL.
PEOPLE LOSE ARMS ALL THE TIME.

24:20.493 --> 24:22.762
IF WE'RE
GOING BY PERCENTAGES,

24:22.762 --> 24:24.897
THE MAJORITY OF THEM'S
ON L.A.P.D.

24:24.897 --> 24:28.434
WELL, SURE, BUT YOU REALLY WANT
TO COMPARE LIMBS TO A TORSO?

24:28.434 --> 24:29.769
YOU THINK THAT'S WISE?

24:29.769 --> 24:32.404
NO ONE'S LIVING TOO LONG
WITHOUT A STOMACH, OKAY?

24:32.404 --> 24:34.774
NO, IF HE -- NO, IF HE HAD
A BIRTH CERTIFICATE,

24:34.774 --> 24:36.809
I WOULDN'T BE NEEDING TO CALL
YOU, WOULD I?

24:36.809 --> 24:39.245
COUSIN DONATED A KIDNEY
TO THIS KID IN WYOMING --

24:39.245 --> 24:40.647
STILL GOING STRONG.

24:40.647 --> 24:42.481
I ASSUME YOUR COUSIN
HAD TWO KIDNEYS, RIGHT?

24:42.481 --> 24:45.585
Tang:
NO, MA'AM. I DIDN'T THINK YOU
HAD A BIG LIST, TO BE HONEST.

24:45.585 --> 24:46.853
ONE HEAD?
I DON'T KNOW.

24:46.853 --> 24:48.721
I GUESS I THOUGHT
YOU'D GIVE A DAMN.

24:48.721 --> 24:51.123
I GUESS I THOUGHT THAT
BECAUSE HE SERVED HIS COUNTRY

24:51.123 --> 24:53.993
AND IT LEFT HIM A WRECK THAT
YOU WOULD WANT TO DO SOMETHING.

24:53.993 --> 24:55.928
I GUESS I THOUGHT THAT
BECAUSE HE'S A HUMAN BEING

24:55.928 --> 24:58.330
LIVING ON THE STREET
LIKE AN ANIMAL THAT
YOU WOULD WANT TO HELP,

24:58.330 --> 25:00.533
BUT I SEE NOW THAT --
THAT YOU HAVE NO INTEREST!

25:00.533 --> 25:02.134
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I HOPE THAT WHEN YOU'RE OLD,

25:02.134 --> 25:04.236
YOU'RE ALONE
LIVING ON THE STREET...

25:04.236 --> 25:06.038
YOU KNOW WHAT?
WE GOT THIS.
...BEGGING FOR FOOD
ON SOME DOORWAY,

25:06.038 --> 25:07.640
AND SOMEONE JUST LIKE YOU
IS THERE TO HELP!

25:07.640 --> 25:08.908
ALL OURS.

25:08.908 --> 25:11.177
YEAH, WELL, YOU HAVE
A FUCKING NICE DAY, TOO!

25:11.177 --> 25:13.479
[ SIGHS ]
DID WE DECIDE ON ANYTHING?

25:13.479 --> 25:15.414
I THINK
THEY'RE GONNA HANDLE IT.

25:15.414 --> 25:17.216
WE GOT IT.

25:17.216 --> 25:20.119
I GOT PATROL OFFICERS OUT THERE
LOOKING FOR HER,

25:20.119 --> 25:23.122
AND I ALSO HAVE SPECIAL AGENT
JAMAICA ON THE CASE.

25:23.122 --> 25:26.292
SHE THINKS SHE KNOWS
WHERE NICOLE MIGHT BE HIDING.

25:27.894 --> 25:30.730
I THOUGHT THE PATROL OFFICER
WAS WATCHING HER.

25:32.098 --> 25:34.333
I SHOULD HAVE
KEPT A CLOSER EYE ON HER.

25:34.333 --> 25:35.702
I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

25:35.702 --> 25:38.104
MOM JUST WON'T GIVE UP.

25:38.104 --> 25:41.173
STILL KEEPS SAYING
SHE DID IT.

25:41.173 --> 25:42.709
THAT'S NO SURPRISE.

25:42.709 --> 25:43.910
REALLY?

25:43.910 --> 25:45.144
SURE.

25:45.144 --> 25:48.114
YOU HAVE KIDS, YOU DO WHATEVER
YOU NEED TO DO FOR THEM.

25:48.114 --> 25:50.482
EVEN ADMIT TO A MURDER
YOU DIDN'T DO?

25:50.482 --> 25:53.485
YEAH, ADMIT TO A MURDER,
YOU KNOW, COMMIT A MURDER --

25:53.485 --> 25:54.553
WHATEVER IT TAKES.

25:54.553 --> 25:56.055
THEY'RE YOUR
RESPONSIBILITY.

25:56.055 --> 25:58.224
YOU WANT TO MAKE SURE
THEY'RE SAFE.

25:58.224 --> 25:59.325
THAT'S WHAT MOMS DO.

25:59.325 --> 26:01.327
[ SIGHS ]

26:01.327 --> 26:03.863
YOU -- YOU OKAY?

26:05.231 --> 26:06.999
WELL, YEAH. WHY?

26:06.999 --> 26:09.769
WELL, JUST,
THE DOCTOR AND EVERYTHING.

26:09.769 --> 26:10.970
I'M FINE.

26:10.970 --> 26:12.204
OKAY.

26:12.204 --> 26:14.641
JUST BEEN SICK
A LOT LATELY...

26:14.641 --> 26:17.243
IN THE MORNINGS...

26:17.243 --> 26:19.178
NOT HUNGRY.

26:23.049 --> 26:27.386
NEXT TIME, DON'T
TAKE ANY CHANCES, ALL RIGHT?

26:27.386 --> 26:31.023
FIND ANOTHER WAY TO GET THE
WITNESS TO STICK AROUND, OKAY?

26:31.023 --> 26:34.761
OKAY. YOU'RE RIGHT.
I'M SORRY.

26:34.761 --> 26:36.896
YOU WANT TO SLEEP
WITH SOME GIRL

26:36.896 --> 26:39.766
WHO SMOKES HASH
AND WORKS IN A THRIFT SHOP,

26:39.766 --> 26:41.567
BE MY GUEST,
BUT IF YOU WANT MY ADVICE --

26:41.567 --> 26:42.735
DO I HAVE A CHOICE?

26:42.735 --> 26:44.103
FIND YOURSELF
A NICE, NORMAL GIRL

26:44.103 --> 26:45.471
WHO WANTS TO SETTLE DOWN,
WANTS TO STAY HOME.

26:45.471 --> 26:47.206
DON'T FIND SOME CHICK...
WE'RE CLEAR, WE'RE CLEAR.

26:47.206 --> 26:49.575
...YOU THINK
YOU'RE GONNA CHANGE.
GO, GO, GO. WE'RE CLEAR.

26:49.575 --> 26:51.410
BECAUSE YOU WANT TO KNOW WHAT?
THEY DON'T CHANGE.

26:51.410 --> 26:53.312
I DON'T CARE WHAT THEY TELL YOU.
THEY DO NOT CHANGE.

26:53.312 --> 26:55.614
HERE WE GO.
HERE WE ARE.
SHE'S GONNA KILL HIM.

26:55.614 --> 26:57.483
SHE GOT A KNIFE,
AND SHE'S GONNA KILL HIM.

26:57.483 --> 26:58.885
WHERE?
INSIDE!

26:58.885 --> 27:01.087
[ CAR DOORS SLAM ]

27:02.855 --> 27:04.991
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

27:04.991 --> 27:07.093
WHOA, MA'AM, MA'AM!
PUT DOWN THE KNIFE!

27:07.093 --> 27:08.995
PUT DOWN THE KNIFE!!
PUT IT DOWN!

27:08.995 --> 27:11.297
I DON'T NEED A KNIFE.

27:11.297 --> 27:13.565
I CAN TAKE HIM OUT
WITH MY OWN BARE HANDS.

27:13.565 --> 27:15.401
IT'S NOT EVEN ILLEGAL.

27:15.401 --> 27:16.969
ACTUALLY...

27:16.969 --> 27:17.636
WHOA.

27:17.636 --> 27:18.570
JESUS.

27:18.570 --> 27:20.072
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

27:20.072 --> 27:21.640
JESUS.

27:24.476 --> 27:26.012
AAH!

27:27.880 --> 27:30.482
ADAM-36.
I NEED AN R/A AT MY LOCATION.

27:30.482 --> 27:34.386
I GOT A CHILD, APPROXIMATELY 6,
IN A POOL, NOT MOVING.

27:34.386 --> 27:36.088
[ GRUNTING ]

27:45.231 --> 27:46.265
COME ON. COME ON.

27:48.500 --> 27:49.535
MOMMY! MOMMY!

27:49.535 --> 27:51.137
[ BOTH CRYING ]
MOMMY!

27:51.137 --> 27:53.505
OKAY, LET HER BREATHE, LET HER
BREATHE, LET HER BREATHE.

27:53.505 --> 27:56.608
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO BE WATCHING
HER, YOU FAT SHIT!

27:56.608 --> 27:58.577
Man: PROBABLY
NOT EVEN MINE, ANYWAY!

27:58.577 --> 28:01.213
HEY! COOL OFF
WITH YOUR KID HERE.

28:05.584 --> 28:06.618
[ STAMMERS ]

28:06.618 --> 28:08.888
WHAT -- NO.

28:08.888 --> 28:11.290
YOU'RE THE FIFTH PERSON
I'VE BEEN TRANSFERRED TO.

28:11.290 --> 28:13.726
YEAH, WELL, YOU'VE BEEN
INCREDIBLY UNHELPFUL.

28:13.726 --> 28:16.095
THANKS FOR NOTHING.

28:16.095 --> 28:18.497
GOING PRETTY FAR OUT OF YOUR WAY
TO HELP THIS GUY.

28:18.497 --> 28:20.632
YEAH, WELL,
I'M NOT GETTING ANYWHERE.

28:20.632 --> 28:22.134
SO, WHAT WAS IT?

28:22.134 --> 28:25.905
CHARMING DEMEANOR, THE SMELL
OF CHEAP WINE ON HIS CLOTHES,

28:25.905 --> 28:28.775
THOSE MILKY-BROWN
BLOODSHOT EYES?

28:29.976 --> 28:31.844
HE'S A MARINE.

28:35.081 --> 28:36.783
YOU IN THE SERVICE?

28:36.783 --> 28:38.851
ME? NO.

28:40.219 --> 28:41.888
MY DAD.

28:42.922 --> 28:45.191
SEMPER FI. YOU KNOW.

28:45.191 --> 28:46.158
[ SIGHS ]

28:46.158 --> 28:47.860
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
MAKE US RESCUE

28:47.860 --> 28:49.962
EVERY MARINE WE COME ACROSS,
ARE YOU?

28:49.962 --> 28:52.398
NEVER LEAVE
ANYONE BEHIND.

28:56.936 --> 28:59.405
TAKE A LEFT UP HERE
ON LAS PALMAS.

28:59.405 --> 29:01.140
WHAT?

29:01.140 --> 29:02.141
TAKE A LEFT.

29:02.141 --> 29:03.042
WHY?

29:03.042 --> 29:05.577
[ CHUCKLES ]
JUST TAKE A LEFT.

29:05.577 --> 29:06.913
[ SIGHS ]

29:11.183 --> 29:12.885
[ SIGHS ]

29:14.386 --> 29:16.188
HEY!

29:16.188 --> 29:18.024
TOM?

29:19.158 --> 29:19.959
HI, TOM.

29:19.959 --> 29:22.161
HEY, BUDDY.

29:22.161 --> 29:22.995
YEAH?

29:22.995 --> 29:25.231
HI.
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

29:26.098 --> 29:29.969
HEY, WE'RE GONNA
TAKE YOUR PICTURE, OKAY?

29:29.969 --> 29:32.071
I'M GONNA HELP YOU UP.
COME ON.

29:32.071 --> 29:34.106
LET'S SIT UP
FOR A LITTLE BIT.

29:34.106 --> 29:36.308
THERE WE GO.
ALL RIGHT.

29:36.308 --> 29:37.844
I'M GONNA
TAKE YOUR HAT OFF, OKAY?

29:37.844 --> 29:39.411
MM.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

29:39.411 --> 29:42.314
I'M JUST GONNA COMB YOUR HAIR.
ALL RIGHT?

29:42.314 --> 29:43.282
YEAH.

29:43.282 --> 29:44.884
John:
JUST FOR THE PICTURE, OKAY?

29:44.884 --> 29:47.219
OKAY.

29:47.219 --> 29:49.221
THERE YOU GO.
YOU CAN HOLD ONTO IT.

29:51.958 --> 29:52.959
THERE WE GO.

29:52.959 --> 29:54.426
LOOK AT THAT.

29:54.426 --> 29:55.427
LOOKS GOOD.

29:55.427 --> 29:57.163
YOU'RE A GOOD-LOOKING
MAN, TOM.

29:57.163 --> 29:59.431
JUST A SECOND --
I'M JUST GONNA WIPE...

29:59.431 --> 30:00.366
THERE WE GO.

30:00.366 --> 30:02.701
MM.
YEAH, THAT FEELS GOOD.

30:02.701 --> 30:04.937
YEAH,
GET THIS UP IN HERE.

30:04.937 --> 30:07.273
YEAH, THAT FEELS --
SMELLS GOOD.

30:07.273 --> 30:08.207
HMM?

30:08.207 --> 30:09.808
ALL RIGHT, TOM.
LOOK AT ME.

30:09.808 --> 30:11.610
GIVE ME A SMILE.

30:11.610 --> 30:13.045
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

30:13.045 --> 30:15.781
THERE YOU GO.
ALL RIGHT, LET'S HAVE ONE MORE.

30:15.781 --> 30:17.917
ARE YOU SERIOUS?
SERIOUS TOM?

30:17.917 --> 30:20.887
LET'S GET SOME SERIOUS --
SERIOUS MARINE TOM.

30:20.887 --> 30:23.622
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]
THERE WE GO.

30:23.622 --> 30:25.858
BETTER GET ME FOR THIS.

30:25.858 --> 30:28.060
WHAT IS THAT?

30:29.595 --> 30:31.597
Ben: [ LAUGHS ]

30:31.597 --> 30:32.899
RIGHT.

30:34.033 --> 30:35.501
VERY FUNNY.

30:35.501 --> 30:37.103
[ IMITATES DOG
BARKING AND SNARLING ]

30:37.103 --> 30:39.171
NICE, NICE, NICE.
GET OUT OF HERE.

30:39.171 --> 30:40.873
THAT'S FUNNY.
[ LAUGHS ]

30:40.873 --> 30:42.341
[ LAUGHS ]

30:42.341 --> 30:45.011
I'M GONNA CALL AGAIN AND SEE
IF HE'S OUT OF SURGERY YET.

30:45.011 --> 30:48.080
HEY, I DIDN'T PUNCH THE DOG
IN THE FACE, AT LEAST.

30:48.080 --> 30:49.515
WELL, THAT'S FUNNY,
ACTUALLY.

30:49.515 --> 30:51.317
YOU REALLY
GOING THROUGH WITH THIS?

30:51.317 --> 30:53.953
YOU WANT TO PUT HIM DOWN,
GO AHEAD. PUT THE NEEDLE IN.

30:53.953 --> 30:55.721
I'LL DRIVE YOU
OVER THERE MYSELF.

30:55.721 --> 30:56.722
HEY.

30:56.722 --> 30:58.257
"RAMMY."

30:58.257 --> 30:59.458
ASSHOLE.

30:59.458 --> 31:00.626
"RAMMY!"

31:00.626 --> 31:02.728
ROSA!

31:02.728 --> 31:05.731
THE POLICE!

31:05.731 --> 31:07.533
HOW'S IT GOING, FELLAS?

31:07.533 --> 31:08.834
ALL RIGHT.

31:08.834 --> 31:11.003
HOW'S THE FAKE I.D. BUSINESS?
STILL GOING STRONG?

31:11.003 --> 31:13.205
[ MACHINE RATTLING ]

31:13.205 --> 31:15.674
SEE THAT?
OLD SCHOOL.

31:15.674 --> 31:19.078
HOPE YOU PUT THAT BITCH AWAY
FOR LIFE, KILLING MY MAN.

31:19.078 --> 31:20.712
YOUR MAN
WAS 50 YEARS OLD.

31:20.712 --> 31:23.749
SO?
LOOK, TOLD YOU SO.

31:23.749 --> 31:26.818
KNEW I COULD DO A BETTER JOB
OF FINDING HER THAN YOU ALL.

31:26.818 --> 31:28.520
NICOLE? WAIT.

31:28.520 --> 31:29.488
WAIT!

31:29.488 --> 31:32.024
Ruben:
OH, OH. I'LL GET IN THE CAR.

31:32.024 --> 31:34.393
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

31:34.393 --> 31:35.962
[ GRUNTS ]

31:47.839 --> 31:50.309
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

31:50.309 --> 31:53.312
KING 54 REQUESTING BACKUP
AT WILSHIRE AND MacARTHUR PARK.

31:53.312 --> 31:55.881
DISPATCHER:
54, we have officers responding.

31:55.881 --> 31:57.316
What's your location?

31:57.316 --> 31:59.185
HEADED SOUTH ON PARK VIEW.

31:59.185 --> 32:01.853
Lydia: NICOLE, STOP!

32:01.853 --> 32:04.423
THERE THEY ARE. THERE THEY ARE.
HERE WE GO. HERE WE GO.

32:04.423 --> 32:06.125
I'M GOING NORTH
ON CORONADO.

32:08.660 --> 32:10.562
NICOLE!

32:10.562 --> 32:12.564
[ BOTH PANTING ]

32:16.735 --> 32:19.638
I RUINED EVERYTHING.

32:19.638 --> 32:20.906
[ CRYING ]

32:20.906 --> 32:22.808
LET ME HELP YOU.

32:22.808 --> 32:23.942
OKAY?

32:23.942 --> 32:25.677
I CAN HELP YOU.

32:25.677 --> 32:27.013
AAH!
UGH!

32:27.013 --> 32:28.780
[ SIREN WAILING ]
AH, SHIT.

32:28.780 --> 32:30.182
UGH.

32:30.182 --> 32:32.184
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

32:42.228 --> 32:44.363
HEY! STOP! STOP!

32:44.363 --> 32:46.098
NICOLE!
NICOLE, STOP THE CAR!

32:46.098 --> 32:48.534
STOP!
STOP THE CAR, NICOLE!

32:48.534 --> 32:50.202
NICOLE!

32:52.338 --> 32:53.972
SHIT.
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

32:53.972 --> 32:55.707
[ CRYING ]

32:58.110 --> 32:59.345
YOU OKAY?

32:59.345 --> 33:00.279
YEAH.

33:00.279 --> 33:02.248
CALL AN AMBULANCE.

33:02.248 --> 33:04.550
ALL RIGHT, SWEETIE.

33:09.288 --> 33:12.458
I'M IN TROUBLE
AGAIN, HUH?

33:12.458 --> 33:15.161
YEAH.

33:15.161 --> 33:18.164
HE TOLD ME HE LOVED ME.

33:18.164 --> 33:19.731
WHAT HAPPENED, SWEETIE?

33:19.731 --> 33:22.434
DID YOU AND BRIAN
HAVE AN ARGUMENT?

33:22.434 --> 33:26.172
I CAUGHT HIM
WITH JAMAICA.

33:26.172 --> 33:28.140
HE DENIED IT.

33:29.708 --> 33:32.311
BUT I KNOW WHAT I SAW.

33:32.311 --> 33:34.146
IT'S ALL OVER NOW,

33:34.146 --> 33:35.881
ISN'T IT?

33:35.881 --> 33:37.249
[ SIGHS ]

33:37.249 --> 33:40.419
WHY DON'T THEY
JUST LET ME DIE?

33:40.419 --> 33:43.689
EVERYBODY WOULD BE BETTER OFF
WITHOUT ME.

33:43.689 --> 33:45.957
NOBODY WANTS ME.

33:45.957 --> 33:47.993
THAT IS NOT TRUE.

33:47.993 --> 33:49.828
YOUR MOTHER IS OUT THERE
RIGHT NOW

33:49.828 --> 33:52.731
CLAIMING THAT SHE'S THE ONE
THAT KILLED MR. MONROE.

33:52.731 --> 33:55.301
SHE'S WILLING TO GO TO PRISON
FOR YOU.

33:55.301 --> 33:58.537
I RUINED HER LIFE.
SHE HATES ME.

33:59.838 --> 34:01.540
[ SIGHS ]

34:01.540 --> 34:05.744
HAVE YOU EVER SEEN YOUR MOM'S
EYES WHEN SHE TALKS ABOUT YOU?

34:07.079 --> 34:11.183
NICOLE,
HER ENTIRE FACE LIGHTS UP.

34:11.183 --> 34:15.321
IT'S LIKE HER LIFE STARTED
WHEN YOU WERE BORN.

34:15.321 --> 34:17.623
SHE'S NOT
AFRAID OF ANYTHING

34:17.623 --> 34:21.627
AS LONG AS SHE KNOWS
THAT YOU'RE OKAY.

34:22.728 --> 34:25.197
NOTHING
IN THIS WORLD MATTERS.

34:25.197 --> 34:27.499
NOTHING MATTERS TO HER
BUT YOU.

34:29.935 --> 34:31.970
I PROMISE YOU, SWEETIE.

34:31.970 --> 34:34.706
YOU MATTER.

34:37.143 --> 34:38.944
Tom: HMM.
Tang: HEY, TOM.

34:38.944 --> 34:41.113
HEY.
HOW YOU DOING?

34:41.113 --> 34:42.148
GOOD.

34:42.148 --> 34:45.584
HEY.
LOOK WHAT I GOT YOU HERE.

34:45.584 --> 34:50.189
YOU HAVE A VIDEO MEMBERSHIP NOW,
YOU'VE GOT A GYM MEMBERSHIP,

34:50.189 --> 34:53.325
AND YOU'VE GOT
A MEMBERSHIP TO YOGA OM.

34:53.325 --> 34:55.161
HUH?
NOT BAD, RIGHT?

34:55.161 --> 34:56.295
THAT AIN'T ME.

34:56.295 --> 34:58.497
[ CHUCKLES ]
John: WELL, SURE IT IS.

34:58.497 --> 35:01.967
I DON'T KNOW WHO THIS IS,
BUT THAT AIN'T -- THAT AIN'T ME.

35:01.967 --> 35:04.170
[ LAUGHS MANIACALLY ]

35:11.710 --> 35:13.111
OKAY, TOM.

35:13.111 --> 35:15.113
THAT AIN'T ME.

35:15.113 --> 35:16.448
I DON'T KNOW WHO IT IS.

35:16.448 --> 35:19.050
TOM, HANG ON ONE SECOND.
HANG ON, BUDDY.

35:19.050 --> 35:20.219
Tang: HEY, TOM.

35:20.219 --> 35:22.020
THAT -- THAT AIN'T --
NO, NO.

35:22.020 --> 35:23.121
OKAY. ALL RIGHT.

35:23.121 --> 35:24.656
TOM, TOM.
HANG ON, BUDDY.

35:24.656 --> 35:26.658
YOU KNOW
WHAT WE'RE GONNA DO?

35:26.658 --> 35:29.728
I'LL GET THAT FOR YOU.
I'LL GET THAT.

35:29.728 --> 35:31.663
AHH.

35:31.663 --> 35:33.532
THAT'S NOT ME.

35:33.532 --> 35:34.466
OKAY.

35:34.466 --> 35:38.103
THAT'S NOT ME.
THAT'S NOT ME.

35:38.103 --> 35:39.538
OKAY, LOOK, TOM?
THAT'S NOT ME.

35:39.538 --> 35:41.673
WE'RE GONNA MOVE YOU
DOWN THE STREET, ALL RIGHT?

35:41.673 --> 35:42.674
THAT'S NOT ME.

35:42.674 --> 35:44.243
THIS GUY'S
TRYING TO RUN A BUSINESS,

35:44.243 --> 35:46.178
AND WE WANT TO BE FAIR TO HIM,
ALL RIGHT?

35:46.178 --> 35:47.546
THAT'S NOT ME.
IT'S OKAY.

35:47.546 --> 35:49.448
THAT'S NOT ME.
THAT'S NOT ME.
IT'S OKAY.

35:49.448 --> 35:52.984
OKAY, SO WE'RE JUST GONNA
MOVE YOU, ALL RIGHT?

35:52.984 --> 35:55.854
TOM? LOOK AT ME.

35:55.854 --> 35:57.723
LOOK AT ME.

35:58.957 --> 36:00.492
HEY, BUDDY.

36:07.766 --> 36:09.000
ALL RIGHT.

36:09.000 --> 36:10.736
DON'T WORRY. I'M GONNA TAKE
SOME OF YOUR STUFF, OKAY?

36:10.736 --> 36:12.271
WE'LL COME BACK.
WE'LL GET IT ALL.

36:12.271 --> 36:13.772
THAT'S NOT ME.
OKAY.

36:13.772 --> 36:15.006
THAT'S NOT ME.

36:15.006 --> 36:17.243
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I DON'T THINK THAT IS YOU, TOM.

36:17.243 --> 36:18.310
I THINK YOU'RE RIGHT.

36:18.310 --> 36:19.645
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S ME.

36:19.645 --> 36:21.513
YOU OKAY?
WHO'S THAT?

36:21.513 --> 36:24.783
WHO'S THIS?
WHO'S THIS?

36:24.783 --> 36:26.685
WHO'S THAT?

36:30.356 --> 36:31.823
SOMETHING HAPPEN?

36:31.823 --> 36:33.325
NO. NO, HE'S FINE.

36:33.325 --> 36:36.228
UH, SAMMY,
THIS IS JUAN ALVAREZ.

36:36.228 --> 36:38.764
HE'S PACO'S OWNER.

36:38.764 --> 36:40.599
Sammy: PACO?

36:40.599 --> 36:42.401
SEГ‘OR.

36:42.401 --> 36:45.203
MUCHAS GRACIAS, SEГ‘OR.
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

36:51.843 --> 36:53.479
[ CHUCKLES ]
HE SAYS "THANK YOU."

36:53.479 --> 36:55.247
HE SAID "THANK YOU."
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

36:55.247 --> 36:56.715
IT'S HIS
GRANDDAUGHTER'S DOG.

36:56.715 --> 36:59.818
SHE'S ALWAYS TAKING
HIS COLLAR OFF TO WASH HIM.

37:03.622 --> 37:06.592
[ SIGHS ] SO, UH,
HE CAN PAY THE BILL, RIGHT?

37:06.592 --> 37:09.295
HE LOOK LIKE
HE CAN PAY THE BILL?

37:09.295 --> 37:12.030
WHAT?

37:12.030 --> 37:14.500
[ LAUGHING ]

37:14.500 --> 37:16.402
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

37:16.402 --> 37:18.504
I'VE PREPARED THE BILL.

37:18.504 --> 37:21.707
UH, WILL YOU BE PAYING
BY CREDIT CARD OR CHECK?

37:21.707 --> 37:23.742
MUCHAS GRACIAS.
WHAT?!

37:24.810 --> 37:25.644
IS SHE OKAY?

37:25.644 --> 37:27.513
YES, SHE'S GONNA BE FINE.

37:27.513 --> 37:30.215
THEY JUST TOOK HER OFF
TO SURGERY.

37:30.215 --> 37:31.850
YOU ARREST HER?

37:31.850 --> 37:33.719
YEAH.

37:34.986 --> 37:36.522
WHEN CAN I SEE HER?

37:36.522 --> 37:40.726
THEY'LL COME AND GET YOU
AS SOON AS SHE COMES OUT.

37:40.726 --> 37:43.194
YOU GONNA ARREST ME
FOR LYING TO YOU?

37:43.194 --> 37:45.531
NO. NO.

37:47.132 --> 37:48.400
DID SHE HURT YOU?

37:48.400 --> 37:53.472
IT'S NOTHING SERIOUS,
JUST A FEW STITCHES.

37:54.406 --> 37:55.874
[ CRYING ]

37:55.874 --> 37:58.744
MY BABY WAS NOT BORN
WITH THE STARS ON HER SIDE.

37:58.744 --> 38:01.012
[ SIGHS ]

38:01.012 --> 38:03.281
AND SHE'S GONNA MAKE IT.

38:03.281 --> 38:04.816
YEAH.

38:04.816 --> 38:09.154
SOMETIMES
LIFE DEALS YOU A TOUGH HAND.

38:09.154 --> 38:11.222
YOU'LL GET THROUGH IT.

38:11.222 --> 38:13.024
ME?

38:13.024 --> 38:16.595
[ SCOFFS ]
I GOT THE BEST HAND THERE IS.

38:16.595 --> 38:19.665
LIKE I SAID,
GOD GIVES YOU THE TEST YOU NEED.

38:22.534 --> 38:25.136
NICOLE HAS BEEN
GOOD FOR YOU?

38:26.372 --> 38:30.308
BEFORE I HAD MY DAUGHTER,
I WAS FLOATING THROUGH LIFE.

38:30.308 --> 38:32.711
I WAS LIKE A --
LIKE A LITTLE BIRD.

38:32.711 --> 38:36.582
DIFFERENT OUTFIT EVERY DAY,
GETTING PROMOTIONS,

38:36.582 --> 38:39.351
KEEPING UP
WITH THE MOVIES AND MAGAZINES.

38:39.351 --> 38:41.753
THAT'S WHAT WAS
IMPORTANT TO ME.

38:45.457 --> 38:47.359
WHAT ARE YOU NOW?

38:47.359 --> 38:50.061
HMM.

38:50.061 --> 38:53.499
I'M A ROCK.

38:53.499 --> 38:55.867
I KNOW WHAT MY LIFE
IS ABOUT.

38:57.268 --> 39:00.906
AND I WOULDN'T CHANGE THAT
FOR ANYTHING IN THE WORLD.

39:04.543 --> 39:06.812
[ CRYING ]

39:08.547 --> 39:10.081
Realtor:
OFFICER SHERMAN, HI.

39:10.081 --> 39:12.484
I HOPE I HAVEN'T
KEPT YOU WAITING LONG.

39:12.484 --> 39:13.719
Ben: JUST GOT HERE.

39:13.719 --> 39:17.789
OKAY, WELL,
LET'S SHOW YOU AROUND.

39:30.769 --> 39:33.505
Ruben:
SO, WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

39:33.505 --> 39:35.741
HUH?
COVENANT HOUSE?

39:35.741 --> 39:37.375
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]
YEAH.

39:37.375 --> 39:38.644
BUT I'LL TAKE HER.

39:38.644 --> 39:41.112
YOU GO AND HAVE DINNER
WITH YOUR FAMILY.

39:41.112 --> 39:42.448
WELL, THANK YOU, PARTNER.

39:42.448 --> 39:43.582
WELCOME.

39:43.582 --> 39:45.617
I'M GLAD
YOU'RE FEELING BETTER --

39:45.617 --> 39:47.285
THE DOCTOR
AND EVERYTHING.

39:47.285 --> 39:48.520
I THOUGHT MAYBE WITH YOU

39:48.520 --> 39:50.355
BEING SICK
IN THE MORNING AND ALL,

39:50.355 --> 39:53.191
THAT YOU MIGHT BE,
UH, YOU KNOW...

39:53.191 --> 39:54.359
PREGNANT.

39:54.359 --> 39:57.095
THAT'S YOU
BEING A DETECTIVE?

39:57.095 --> 39:59.164
DEDUCING AND INTUITION.

39:59.164 --> 40:00.666
MM-HMM.
YES.

40:00.666 --> 40:04.603
YOU MAY WANT TO WORK ON
THAT INTUITION PART.

40:07.105 --> 40:08.273
RIGHT.

40:08.273 --> 40:09.407
RIGHT.

40:09.407 --> 40:10.542
OKAY.

40:10.542 --> 40:11.543
OKAY.

40:11.543 --> 40:12.978
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

40:12.978 --> 40:14.412
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

40:21.052 --> 40:25.457
JAMAICA, CAN I ASK YOU
A PERSONAL QUESTION?

40:29.160 --> 40:30.662
GO AHEAD.

40:30.662 --> 40:33.765
WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR FAMILY?

40:37.168 --> 40:39.170
I HAVE A MOM,

40:39.170 --> 40:43.174
BUT SHE DON'T WANT TO...

40:43.174 --> 40:46.244
WELL, SHE LIKES TO PARTY.

40:46.244 --> 40:47.979
I MEAN,
I SEE HER SOMETIMES.

40:47.979 --> 40:52.183
WHEN SHE'S GOT SOME MONEY,
SHE'D TAKE ME SHOPPING...

40:52.183 --> 40:54.720
FOR CLOTHES, MAKEUP.

40:54.720 --> 40:57.923
SHE LIKES TO LOOK GOOD,
HAVE FUN.

41:02.594 --> 41:05.196
YOU AIN'T INTO THAT STUFF,
ARE YOU?

41:06.732 --> 41:09.467
NO, NOT REALLY.

41:09.467 --> 41:12.037
YOU GOT KIDS?

41:16.942 --> 41:18.910
SOON.

41:21.747 --> 41:24.616
THEY GONNA BE
LUCKY KIDS.
